G2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/lolnot-my-title-old-picture-but-fun-interview</guid></item><item><title>逆光刻技术的进步和挑战：基于人工智能的方法回顾</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/advancements-and-challenges-in-inverse-lithography-technology-a-review-of-artificial-intelligence-based-approaches</link><description>逆光刻采用了完全不同的方法。 ILT 不是从所需的电路图案开始并对其进行调整以补偿光学失真，而是向后工作。它问道：“在光线发生扭曲作用后，什么样的掩模图案可以产生我们想要的确切形状？”这就像设计一面游乐园镜子，让你的倒影看起来完全正常。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/advancements-and-challenges-in-inverse-lithography-technology-a-review-of-artificial-intelligence-based-approaches.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/advancements-and-challenges-in-inverse-lithography-technology-a-review-of-artificial-intelligence-based-approaches</guid></item><item><title>新型阿片类药物可有效缓解疼痛，且无典型副作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/novel-opioid-offers-potent-pain-relief-without-classic-side-effects</link><description>研究人员发现了一种新型合成阿片类药物，可以在临床前模型中有效缓解疼痛，且不会产生限制当前阿片类药物治疗的许多危险副作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/novel-opioid-offers-potent-pain-relief-without-classic-side-effects.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:11:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/novel-opioid-offers-potent-pain-relief-without-classic-side-effects</guid></item><item><title>实验药物使胰腺癌的一年生存率翻倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/experimental-drug-doubles-one-year-survival-in-pancreatic-cancer</link><description>一种新药的作用是使肿瘤对化疗和免疫系统更敏感，在一项试验中提高了晚期胰腺癌患者的生存率。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/experimental-drug-doubles-one-year-survival-in-pancreatic-cancer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:56:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/experimental-drug-doubles-one-year-survival-in-pancreatic-cancer</guid></item><item><title>前沿： 背景：</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/frontiers-background</link><description>绿原酸 (CGA) 和牛磺酸是众所周知的抗氧化化合物，据报道可以减少皮肤细胞衰老。然而，其皮肤保护作用的生物学机制仍不清楚。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/frontiers3.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/frontiers-background</guid></item><item><title>心房颤动的导管消融和口服抗凝药</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/catheter-ablation-and-oral-anticoagulation-in-atrial-fibrillation</link><description>在患有心房颤动和近期中风的患者中，与标准治疗相比，在口服抗凝药物中加入导管消融并没有显着减少中风复发、全身性栓塞、死亡或因心力衰竭住院的情况。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/catheter-ablation-and-oral-anticoagulation-in-atrial-fibrillation.png" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/catheter-ablation-and-oral-anticoagulation-in-atrial-fibrillation</guid></item><item><title>升空</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/lift-off</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 23:11:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/lift-off</guid></item></channel></rss>